                            <comment id="99264" author="yujian" created="Sat, 15 Nov 2014 02:54:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Test results showed that by increasing the time in max_recovery_time() in test framework, the failures in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5900&quot; title=&quot;replay-dual test_11: rm: cannot remove `/mnt/lustre/f11.replay-dual-[1-5]&amp;#39;: No such file or directory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5900&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5900&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5901&quot; title=&quot;replay-dual test_15a: import is not in FULL state&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5901&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5901&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; were resolved. And by adding some margin into the recovery time comparison condition, the failure in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5902&quot; title=&quot;replay-dual test_20: FAIL: recovery time is growing 215 &amp;gt; 107&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5902&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5902&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was resolved.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
