                            <comment id="97696" author="yujian" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 15:11:48 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11213/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11213/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I tried to manually run replay-vbr test and found it finally passed and took about 8 hours:&lt;br/&gt;
