&lt;p&gt;Among the sub-tests, test 7e took 3876s, which exceeded the 3600s timeout value set by autotest system. That was why the test was stopped in autotest runs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="97475" author="morrone" created="Fri, 24 Oct 2014 21:52:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12365&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12365&lt;/a&gt; on top of LLNL&apos;s 2.5.3-1chaos tag, and saw lots of problems.  I don&apos;t know if they were actually cause by it or not.  Experience is recorded in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5805&quot; title=&quot;tgt_recov blocked and &amp;quot;waking for gap in transno&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5805&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5805&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="97425" author="yujian" created="Fri, 24 Oct 2014 17:32:48 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11213/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11213/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The above patch introduced regression failure in replay-vbr test 7e.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On master branch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/92fe44e0-5b80-11e4-a35f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/92fe44e0-5b80-11e4-a35f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On b2_5 branch:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4d02235e-59c2-11e4-aa32-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/4d02235e-59c2-11e4-aa32-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/25213bfe-59c2-11e4-aa32-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/25213bfe-59c2-11e4-aa32-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
